==English==
===Noun===
'''bobbar'''

#(''Northern English slang'') Excrement.
#(''Northern English slang'') Something that is rubbish, useless, nonsense.
#(''Northern English slang'') Something of poor quality.

===Verb===
'''to bobbar'''

#(''Northern English slang'') To defecate.

===Usage note===
Used in the North of England, especially in Sheffield and Barnsley.

